body:
Hi.



The error about "LookupFolder_Daylighting" component was appeared.



I set a folder(C:\Grasshopper\study\test) to the working directory.

And I found the files in the folder I defined like the image.



Why cannot clear this error message?



Thank you.

replies.body:
Natchan,

You need to reinsert both HB_runDaylightAnalysis and HB_LookupFolder_Daylighting assuming you updated from the github.

Both of them have changed in the number of input/output items.

I'm sure that will fix the issue.

-A.

Hi, Abraham.



I reinsert the components,and the error was vanished.



thank you for your kind.
